---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';

const serviceTitle = 'Custom Automation Solutions';
const metadata = {
  title: `${serviceTitle} - Capybara Studios`,
  description: `Tailored automation systems designed to solve your unique business challenges and unlock specific growth opportunities.`,
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <section class="py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <header class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tighter tracking-tighter font-heading dark:text-gray-200">
          {serviceTitle}
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-muted dark:text-slate-300">
          Bespoke automation systems built to your exact specifications, addressing complex challenges and unique
          operational needs.
        </p>
      </header>

      <article class="prose dark:prose-invert lg:prose-xl mx-auto">
        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
            The Challenge: When Off-the-Shelf Isn't Enough
          </h2>
          <p>
            Do your business processes have unique complexities that standard automation tools can't quite handle?
            Perhaps you're looking to integrate disparate legacy systems, require highly specialized workflows, or have
            specific data security and sovereignty needs that demand a tailored approach. Common scenarios where custom
            solutions shine include:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
            <li>
              Complex, multi-step workflows that span various departments or unique software.
              <li>
                Need for deep integration with proprietary or legacy systems.
                <li>
                  Stringent data security, compliance, or data residency requirements.
                  <li>
                    Desire for a fully owned and controlled automation infrastructure.
                    <li>
                      Scaling automation efforts beyond the capacities of standard SaaS platforms.
                      <li>Unique business models or operational processes that require a bespoke system.</li>
                    </li>

                    <section class="mb-12">
                      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
                        The Capybara Studios Way: Your Vision, Automated
                      </h2>
                      <p>
                        Our Custom Automation Solutions service is designed for businesses that need more than a
                        one-size-fits-all approach. We work closely with you to understand your specific challenges and
                        objectives, then design and build a tailored automation system from the ground up, or by heavily
                        customizing existing platforms. Our process involves:
                      </p>
                      <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 space-y-3">
                        <li>
                          <strong>In-Depth Consultation & Needs Analysis:</strong> We start with a deep dive into your requirements,
                          existing infrastructure, and desired outcomes to ensure we fully understand the problem we're solving.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                          <strong>Solution Architecture & Design:</strong> We architect a custom solution, selecting the
                          right technologies and approaches. This might involve leveraging powerful open-source platforms
                          like n8n on a dedicated server for maximum control and flexibility, or developing custom scripts
                          and API integrations.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                          <strong>Dedicated Infrastructure (Example: Private n8n Setup):</strong> For clients needing robust
                          control, security, or scalability, we can provision and configure a dedicated automation environment,
                          such as a private n8n instance on a Virtual Private Server (VPS). This offers:
                          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
                            <li>Full data sovereignty and enhanced security.</li>
                            <li>Ability to run resource-intensive or long-running workflows.</li>
                            <li>Custom integrations and extensions.</li>
                            <li>Predictable costs and full ownership.</li>
                          </ul>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                          <strong>Iterative Development & Implementation:</strong> We build your custom solution, involving
                          you in the process for feedback and adjustments to ensure it meets your exact needs.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                          <strong>Comprehensive Onboarding & Documentation:</strong> We provide thorough training and documentation
                          so your team can confidently use and manage the new system.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                          <strong>Ongoing Support & Evolution:</strong> We offer continued support and can help evolve your
                          custom solution as your business grows and your needs change.
                        </li>
                      </ol>
                      <p class="mt-4">
                        If you have a unique challenge or a vision for a specific automation that goes beyond standard
                        offerings, our custom solutions are designed to bring it to life.
                      </p>
                    </section>

                    <div class="mt-12 text-center py-8 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-lg">
                      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
                        Have a Unique Automation Challenge?
                      </h3>
                      <p class="mb-6 text-muted dark:text-slate-300">
                        Let's discuss your specific needs and build a tailored automation solution together.
                      </p>
                      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary text-lg px-8 py-3">Discuss Your Custom Project</a>
                    </div>
                  </li>
                </li>
              </li>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section></Layout
>
